hw6: Inter-Image processing

based on ex11

wheres wally (AKA Waldo). An examination of wally's space on the page

Willem A. (Vlakkies) Schreuder
CSCI4239/5239 Spring 2026

Mostly ripped off from Pete Battaglia (Fall 2009)

compare images lets you examine wally in comparison to the scene

all wallys shows the positions of all wallys from all images

migrate wally takes wally from current image, and migrates him to a new one


Key bindings
  m/M        Cycle through shaders forwards (filters)
  n/N        Cycle through shaders backwards (filters)
  J/K		 Cycle through images
  G/H		 Cycle through images to migrate wally to
  U/I		 Switch shaders, image compare, all wallys, migrate wally
  +/-        Change fraction in mix mode
  a          Toggle crosshairs
  arrows     Pan location
  PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out
  0          Reset view
  ESC        Exit
